freenet.node.fcp
Class ClientGet

java.lang.Object
  freenet.node.fcp.ClientRequest
      freenet.node.fcp.ClientGet
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientBaseCallback, ClientGetCallback, ClientEventListener
public class ClientGet
extends ClientRequest
implements ClientGetCallback, ClientEventListener

A simple client fetch. This can of course fetch arbitrarily large files, including splitfiles, redirects, etc.
